WEBVTT

00:00:15.083 --> 00:00:17.125
Yui, use this.

00:00:19.167 --> 00:00:21.125
I'm going to transfer the code.

00:00:21.250 --> 00:00:24.250
We're about to be teleported.
Daddy, your hand!

00:00:30.833 --> 00:00:33.083
Daddy... Daddy!

00:00:34.708 --> 00:00:36.167
Yui?

00:00:36.167 --> 00:00:40.708
--Where are we?
--I don't know. There's no mapping data.

00:00:41.167 --> 00:00:43.833
--Do you know where Asuna is?
--Yes.

00:00:45.042 --> 00:00:47.750
She's close... Very close.

00:00:49.125 --> 00:00:50.292
This way!

00:01:19.583 --> 00:01:23.125
This is the top of the World Tree?

00:01:25.583 --> 00:01:28.917
The Floating City isn't up here...

00:01:29.292 --> 00:01:33.542
Some "Grand Quest."
Everything was a lie.

00:01:33.542 --> 00:01:35.625
I won't let him get away with this!

00:01:36.875 --> 00:01:41.583
Oh, right...
It can wait until we save Asuna.

00:02:03.667 --> 00:02:09.083
<i>The feelings I've hidden</i>
<i>are crying out in pain</i>

00:02:09.083 --> 00:02:14.583
<i>Holding a sure promise in my hand</i>

00:02:24.750 --> 00:02:35.042
<i>Seeking only a miracle, I wander</i>
<i>through an endless darkness</i>

00:02:35.167 --> 00:02:45.792
<i>If I stay here, I won't</i>
<i>ever see the future again</i>

00:02:45.958 --> 00:02:51.167
<i>Tonight the moon summons me again.</i>
<i>Though I still cannot speak,</i>

00:02:51.167 --> 00:02:54.958
<i>I keep crying out in my heart</i>

00:02:56.083 --> 00:03:01.333
<i>My hidden feelings</i>
<i>are crying out in pain</i>

00:03:01.458 --> 00:03:06.375
<i>Holding a sure promise in my hand</i>

00:03:06.542 --> 00:03:12.083
<i>If I can stay stronger a bit longer,</i>

00:03:12.083 --> 00:03:18.167
<i>I will go beyond</i>
<i>this sky right in front of me</i>

00:03:20.083 --> 00:03:26.625
<i>I will reach out towards</i>
<i>the future ahead of me</i>

00:03:32.042 --> 00:03:36.042
"Gilded Hero"

00:03:47.250 --> 00:03:48.333
Mommy!

00:03:51.417 --> 00:03:52.542
Mommy!

00:04:02.875 --> 00:04:04.083
Mommy!

00:04:05.208 --> 00:04:06.208
Yui!

00:04:07.375 --> 00:04:08.375
Mommy...

00:04:09.375 --> 00:04:10.417
Yui...

00:04:13.292 --> 00:04:15.542
Mommy... Mommy!

00:04:28.333 --> 00:04:29.833
Kirito.

00:04:31.500 --> 00:04:32.625
Asuna.

00:04:37.958 --> 00:04:40.000
I'm sorry I'm late.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:45.750
I believed in you... I knew
you'd come to save me.

00:04:50.708 --> 00:04:53.583
Now, let's go home together.

00:04:54.333 --> 00:04:55.333
Yeah.

00:04:56.500 --> 00:04:59.833
Yui, can you log out Asuna?

00:05:00.583 --> 00:05:07.750
Mommy's status is locked down by complicated codes.
We'll need a system console to dispel them.

00:05:07.750 --> 00:05:10.458
I saw one in the lab--

00:05:14.042 --> 00:05:15.042
What?

00:05:20.542 --> 00:05:23.458
Yui... What's going on?

00:05:26.083 --> 00:05:29.417
Daddy! Mommy!
Be careful...

00:05:29.417 --> 00:05:32.333
Something bad is coming.

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.208
--Yui!
--Yui!

00:05:40.292 --> 00:05:41.417
Asuna...

00:05:50.583 --> 00:05:52.708
What a surprise...

00:05:52.708 --> 00:05:57.083
I didn't expect to see a cockroach
in my little bird's cage.

00:05:57.333 --> 00:05:58.708
Are you...

00:05:58.708 --> 00:06:00.708
...Sugou?

00:06:02.917 --> 00:06:10.333
I'd prefer you not use that name in this world.
Call me His Highness, Fairy King Oberon!

00:06:11.333 --> 00:06:12.792
Kirito!

00:06:13.250 --> 00:06:16.375
How is it? You can barely move, right?

00:06:16.375 --> 00:06:22.500
This is gravity magic, coming out in the
next update. Maybe it's a little overpowered?

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:24.792
Stop it... You coward!

00:06:25.125 --> 00:06:27.583
That said, Kirigaya...

00:06:27.583 --> 00:06:31.042
Or do you prefer Kirito?

00:06:31.500 --> 00:06:34.375
How did you get up here?

00:06:34.625 --> 00:06:37.750
I saw a strange program running just now.

00:06:37.917 --> 00:06:41.208
I flew with these wings...

00:06:42.333 --> 00:06:43.958
It doesn't matter.

00:06:44.125 --> 00:06:48.000
I can just ask your mind directly.

00:06:48.375 --> 00:06:49.625
What?

00:06:49.875 --> 00:06:56.500
You didn't really think I set this
entire thing up for fun, did you?

00:06:57.125 --> 00:07:03.750
Three hundred former SAO players...
Thanks to their dedicated cooperation,

00:07:03.750 --> 00:07:09.792
the fundamental technology for emotion and
thought control is already 80 percent complete.

00:07:09.917 --> 00:07:14.542
I'll achieve what no one ever has,
control of the human soul!

00:07:14.542 --> 00:07:18.583
The power of a god!
And soon, that power will be mine!

00:07:18.583 --> 00:07:22.250
Seriously, thank goodness
for virtual worlds!

00:07:25.250 --> 00:07:26.875
Sugou!

00:07:27.042 --> 00:07:31.208
You'll never get away with this. Never!

00:07:31.792 --> 00:07:37.250
Who's going to stop me?
Sadly, there's no God in this world.

00:07:37.500 --> 00:07:39.542
Except for me!

00:07:40.583 --> 00:07:47.000
Now, before I begin altering your souls,
let's have a fun party!

00:07:56.375 --> 00:07:59.167
You bastard, what are you...

00:08:18.042 --> 00:08:19.042
Now!

00:08:21.917 --> 00:08:28.833
Great! I love it! NPC women
just can't make that face...

00:08:33.333 --> 00:08:40.250
What a lovely smell. Replicating your scent
from the real world was hard.

00:08:40.542 --> 00:08:47.625
I hope you appreciate how much work it took
to get an analyzer into your hospital room...

00:08:47.958 --> 00:08:49.083
Stop it.

00:08:49.625 --> 00:08:51.250
Sugou...

00:08:54.708 --> 00:08:56.250
My, my...

00:08:56.667 --> 00:09:01.875
Onlookers can just grovel
on the ground! Writhing!

00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:06.583
Kirito!

00:09:10.292 --> 00:09:12.250
System command!

00:09:12.250 --> 00:09:16.250
Change pain absorber
from level 10 to level 8.

00:09:20.375 --> 00:09:21.667
Hurts, no?

00:09:21.833 --> 00:09:25.917
I'll gradually let the pain increase,
so look forward to that.

00:09:25.917 --> 00:09:32.000
Of course, below level 3,
it will start to affect your physical body.

00:09:32.333 --> 00:09:33.667
Now then...

00:09:38.250 --> 00:09:40.625
Stop it, Sugou...

00:09:41.667 --> 00:09:43.708
It's all right, Kirito.

00:09:43.875 --> 00:09:46.750
He can't hurt me by doing this.

00:09:48.083 --> 00:09:52.583
That's what I hoped you'd say...
How long will you maintain your pride?

00:09:52.583 --> 00:09:55.208
Thirty minutes? An hour?

00:09:55.208 --> 00:09:59.167
Try to hold on to it as long as you can!

00:10:15.875 --> 00:10:20.083
Shall I tell you what I'm thinking?

00:10:20.417 --> 00:10:25.250
Once I've had my fun here,
I'll go to your hospital room.

00:10:26.083 --> 00:10:33.042
I'll play a recording of today on
a big monitor, and we can enjoy ourselves.

00:10:34.083 --> 00:10:37.125
With your real body.

00:10:49.833 --> 00:10:53.125
S-Sweet...
So sweet!

00:10:53.458 --> 00:10:56.208
Sugou, you bastard!

00:10:56.208 --> 00:10:58.042
Bastard!

00:11:06.042 --> 00:11:10.625
You bastard, I'll kill you!
I'll kill you no matter what!

00:11:24.625 --> 00:11:27.542
<i>Is this my punishment?</i>

00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:31.875
<i>For thinking that I was the</i>
<i>game's strongest hero?</i>

00:11:32.042 --> 00:11:35.542
<i>That I could save Asuna alone?</i>

00:11:36.083 --> 00:11:37.458
<i>Even though</i>

00:11:38.250 --> 00:11:40.917
<i>I have no power at all...</i>

00:11:46.583 --> 00:11:48.250
<i>Are you going to run away?</i>

00:11:50.833 --> 00:11:52.500
<i>Are you going to run away?</i>

00:11:52.667 --> 00:11:56.333
<i>That's not it...</i>
<i>I'm going to accept reality.</i>

00:11:56.333 --> 00:12:01.167
<i>Are you going to surrender?</i>
<i>To the power of a system you once denied.</i>

00:12:01.458 --> 00:12:07.542
<i>I don't have a choice.</i>
<i>I'm a player, and he's a GM.</i>

00:12:07.542 --> 00:12:10.792
Those words make
a mockery of our battle.

00:12:11.583 --> 00:12:15.500
Our battle that proved human
will superior to the system,

00:12:15.500 --> 00:12:19.625
and awakened me to
the possibilities of the future.

00:12:19.792 --> 00:12:21.333
You're...

00:12:23.542 --> 00:12:26.125
<i>Stand up, Kirito!</i>

00:12:39.500 --> 00:12:42.500
Your attacks have no soul...

00:12:42.750 --> 00:12:46.333
The blades in that world hit harder...

00:12:47.458 --> 00:12:49.417
They hurt way more!

00:12:56.875 --> 00:13:01.250
I guess some odd bugs are still left.

00:13:03.250 --> 00:13:05.042
System login...

00:13:05.500 --> 00:13:07.458
ID Heathcliff.

00:13:07.792 --> 00:13:11.042
Wh-What?
What is that ID?

00:13:11.250 --> 00:13:12.833
System command.

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:17.833
Enable administrator privileges.
Set ID Oberon to level 1.

00:13:18.958 --> 00:13:23.000
An ID that outranks mine?
That's impossible!

00:13:23.000 --> 00:13:25.875
I am the ruler! The creator!

00:13:25.875 --> 00:13:28.250
King of this world! God!

00:13:28.250 --> 00:13:29.917
No, you're not.

00:13:30.375 --> 00:13:34.958
You stole it... This world.
And its people.

00:13:34.958 --> 00:13:39.333
You're a king of thieves,
alone upon a stolen throne!

00:13:39.333 --> 00:13:41.750
Y-You stupid kid...

00:13:41.750 --> 00:13:45.417
How... How dare you
talk to me like that?

00:13:45.750 --> 00:13:50.417
System command.
Generate object ID Excalibur.

00:13:52.917 --> 00:13:58.500
Do as I say, you piece of crap!
These... These are God's orders!

00:13:59.083 --> 00:14:01.083
Wait a bit longer, okay?

00:14:01.250 --> 00:14:03.333
I'll end this right away.

00:14:06.208 --> 00:14:08.042
System command!

00:14:08.208 --> 00:14:12.042
Generate object ID Excalibur!

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:18.125
So a single command is all it takes
to summon a legendary weapon?

00:14:26.750 --> 00:14:28.958
It's time to settle the score.

00:14:29.125 --> 00:14:32.500
Between the king of thieves
and a gilded hero!

00:14:33.458 --> 00:14:37.542
System command.
Set pain absorber to level 0.

00:14:38.167 --> 00:14:39.583
Wh-What?

00:14:39.917 --> 00:14:41.208
Don't run away.

00:14:41.458 --> 00:14:44.917
That man never flinched
no matter what happened.

00:14:45.083 --> 00:14:47.708
Not Akihiko Kayaba!

00:14:47.708 --> 00:14:49.375
K-Kaya...

00:14:49.625 --> 00:14:51.000
Kayaba!

00:14:51.167 --> 00:14:54.458
I see... That ID was...

00:14:54.458 --> 00:14:58.875
Why? Why do you still
thwart me, even after death?

00:14:58.875 --> 00:15:03.208
You're always this way!
Acting like you know everything!

00:15:03.208 --> 00:15:05.875
Taking everything I want!

00:15:05.875 --> 00:15:09.500
Sugou... It's not that I can't relate.

00:15:09.500 --> 00:15:13.792
I also lost to him and had
to become his subordinate.

00:15:14.042 --> 00:15:17.625
However, I never wanted to be him.

00:15:18.208 --> 00:15:19.917
Unlike you...

00:15:20.167 --> 00:15:23.000
You goddamned brat!

00:15:31.375 --> 00:15:33.208
Damn it all!

00:15:36.083 --> 00:15:37.292
That hurt!

00:15:39.625 --> 00:15:41.500
Oh, that hurt?

00:15:42.042 --> 00:15:44.625
But you've hurt Asuna

00:15:44.792 --> 00:15:47.000
way more!

00:15:52.375 --> 00:15:53.792
My hand!

00:15:54.125 --> 00:15:57.708
My hand!

00:16:47.375 --> 00:16:49.375
I believed in you.

00:16:50.083 --> 00:16:54.500
No, I still do.
I always have and always will.

00:16:54.500 --> 00:16:59.000
That you're my hero.
That you'll always come save me.

00:17:00.125 --> 00:17:01.667
That isn't true.

00:17:01.833 --> 00:17:05.667
I... I don't have any power at all.

00:17:09.375 --> 00:17:13.250
But I'll do my best to be that way.

00:17:13.792 --> 00:17:14.833
Yeah.

00:17:16.333 --> 00:17:18.958
Now, let's go home.

00:17:21.292 --> 00:17:24.208
It's probably nighttime
in the real world.

00:17:24.375 --> 00:17:27.583
But I'll go to your hospital room soon.

00:17:27.750 --> 00:17:29.000
I'll be waiting.

00:17:29.167 --> 00:17:32.333
You're the first person I want to see.

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:40.250
It's finally over, isn't it?
I can return to the real world.

00:17:40.250 --> 00:17:41.250
"End all services and execute log out."

00:17:41.500 --> 00:17:42.833
That's right.

00:17:43.542 --> 00:17:46.333
You'll be surprised
how much has changed.

00:17:47.333 --> 00:17:51.833
Let's go to all kinds of places
and do all kinds of things.

00:17:51.833 --> 00:17:53.833
Yeah, definitely.

00:18:21.708 --> 00:18:24.625
It's all over now.

00:18:25.208 --> 00:18:26.625
Isn't it?

00:18:28.375 --> 00:18:31.333
You're there, aren't you, Heathcliff?

00:18:32.708 --> 00:18:35.292
It's been a while, Kirito.

00:18:35.292 --> 00:18:36.917
You're alive?

00:18:37.083 --> 00:18:40.583
You could say I am,
or you could say I'm not.

00:18:40.583 --> 00:18:46.625
I am an echo of the mind that
was Akihiko Kayaba. An afterimage.

00:18:46.625 --> 00:18:49.833
As usual, you're not
making much sense.

00:18:50.167 --> 00:18:52.958
Well, I guess I'll thank you.

00:18:53.125 --> 00:18:55.750
--No need for thanks.
--Why?

00:18:55.750 --> 00:19:00.042
Our relationship isn't so close that
we'd exchange favors for free.

00:19:00.042 --> 00:19:02.958
There is a price. Always.

00:19:02.958 --> 00:19:05.250
What do you want me to do?

00:19:14.542 --> 00:19:19.250
--What's this?
--The beginning of a world, "the Seed."

00:19:20.625 --> 00:19:23.167
Once it sprouts,
you'll understand what it is.

00:19:23.333 --> 00:19:28.125
What to do then is up to you.
You can delete and forget it.

00:19:28.292 --> 00:19:33.917
However, if you have any feelings
left for that world besides hatred...

00:19:37.208 --> 00:19:39.042
I'll be going then.

00:19:39.208 --> 00:19:42.042
I hope we meet again, Kirito.

00:19:49.458 --> 00:19:52.250
Yui! Are you okay, Yui?

00:19:52.667 --> 00:19:53.958
Daddy!

00:19:54.125 --> 00:19:56.708
You're safe! I'm so glad...

00:19:56.708 --> 00:20:01.208
Yes. I took shelter in your
NerveGear's local memory.

00:20:01.833 --> 00:20:06.042
--Where's Mommy?
--She went back to the real world.

00:20:06.042 --> 00:20:07.958
Really?

00:20:08.125 --> 00:20:12.250
I'm so glad!
I'm so glad... I really am!

00:20:12.958 --> 00:20:15.333
We'll be back to see you soon.

00:20:15.750 --> 00:20:19.042
But what will happen to this world?

00:20:19.333 --> 00:20:25.042
My core program is inside your
NerveGear. We'll always be together.

00:20:25.958 --> 00:20:29.458
Then I'll be going to
welcome back Mommy.

00:20:29.458 --> 00:20:32.917
Okay, Daddy! I love you!

00:20:47.542 --> 00:20:48.792
"Are you sure you want to log out?"

00:20:59.083 --> 00:21:03.917
I-I'm sorry... You didn't
come back, so I got worried.

00:21:05.042 --> 00:21:07.083
Sorry it took so long.

00:21:07.875 --> 00:21:09.500
Is it all over?

00:21:09.667 --> 00:21:11.792
Yeah, it is.

00:21:11.958 --> 00:21:13.375
Everything.

00:21:14.208 --> 00:21:15.667
That's great!

00:21:19.042 --> 00:21:20.625
Thank you...

00:21:20.625 --> 00:21:23.042
Thank you so much, Sugu.

00:21:23.375 --> 00:21:27.167
I couldn't have done
anything without you.

00:21:27.167 --> 00:21:28.167
No...

00:21:32.542 --> 00:21:38.208
It made me happy to be able
to help you in your world.

00:21:46.708 --> 00:21:49.792
You got Asuna back, didn't you?

00:21:49.792 --> 00:21:51.917
Yeah, finally.

00:21:52.292 --> 00:21:54.208
She's finally back.

00:21:55.042 --> 00:21:56.875
Sugu, I...

00:21:57.375 --> 00:21:58.792
Go see her.

00:21:59.333 --> 00:22:02.167
I'm sure she's waiting for you.

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:11.500
I-It's cold...

00:22:12.333 --> 00:22:13.542
Snow.

00:22:16.458 --> 00:22:17.750
Be careful. Say hi to Asuna for me.

00:22:17.750 --> 00:22:19.625
<i>Higher and higher, I reach out my arms</i>
Be careful. Say hi to Asuna for me.

00:22:19.625 --> 00:22:24.833
<i>Higher and higher, I reach out my arms</i>
Yeah, I'll introduce you properly soon.

00:22:24.833 --> 00:22:34.542
<i>"Surely, surely..."</i>
<i>I'll wish for it once again</i>

00:22:45.917 --> 00:22:52.708
<i>These endless feelings were</i>
<i>swallowed up into my daily life</i>

00:22:53.083 --> 00:22:59.917
<i>Swaying as they</i>
<i>change shape yet again</i>

00:23:00.250 --> 00:23:07.167
<i>Is it too late now? I ask</i>
<i>myself but receive no answer</i>

00:23:07.292 --> 00:23:14.833
<i>It's all up to me now,</i>
<i>both the ending and the beginning</i>

00:23:15.000 --> 00:23:21.917
<i>Higher and higher,</i>
<i>I reach out my arms</i>

00:23:21.917 --> 00:23:29.125
<i>I'm going to spread my wings</i>
<i>and head towards that gentle light</i>

00:23:29.125 --> 00:23:36.542
<i>Carrying the passion</i>
<i>I've lit in my heart</i>

00:23:36.542 --> 00:23:44.750
<i>"Surely, surely..."</i>
<i>I'll wish for it once again</i>

00:23:47.000 --> 00:23:53.110
Next Time: "The World Seed."
